{"tid":2070942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果同立場既分別（泛粉慎入）","createTime":"2020-06-19T12:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T20:05:39.000Z","uid":313692,"like":17,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"530f54aa3f9741697a8376f2f3ce44fd79519bc1","tid":2070942,"uid":313692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SPFFhvh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSPFFhvh.png&h=d9e7e198&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4jZx3D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4jZx3D.png&h=85d1845e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能你覺得冇乜特別，我哋可以再睇埋第二張圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxccS83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxccS83.png&h=28a27c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGfJZO4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGfJZO4.png&h=73aa2b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以原諒我手機cap得唔好先<br />\n<br />\n尋日首席法官任命既投票，我睇蘋果以為泛民係全投棄權，今日睇返立場先知竟然有人投贊成。<br />\n<br />\n然後今日，蘋果到依家都唔肯出街工既報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣嘅蘋果我實在支持唔落。今日開始，我決定取消訂閱，每個月再用一樣嘅錢捐比立場。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">88，蘋果</span></span>"},{"pid":"75556df995111d5205c1b1301ce82e824446e5e3","tid":2070942,"uid":55458,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:42:17.000Z","msg":"分化燈仔快啲咬人啦"},{"pid":"64f754c0eab88f3c13198cdaa0d8bfb0304af16b","tid":2070942,"uid":49336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:44:27.000Z","msg":"樓主自己揀一個：<br />\n熱狗 左膠 五毛 pr公司<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" clas